{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_02_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 無口な二枚貝",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから雫に自信を付けてもらおうと）\n（沢山特訓をしたけど）\n（ほとんど成果が見えなかったな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After that I practiced all kinds of things with Shizuku)\n(to give her confidence‚)\n(but to no avail…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……おかしいな、今日も会話術を学びに行く予定なのに\n雫がまだ来ない……ん？　雫から電話？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s strange. It's time to go to her conversation skills class today‚\nbut she’s not here yet. Huh? A call from Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6299.999999999999,
          "startTime": 17.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10466.666666666666,
          "startTime": 21.366666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "これ以上迷惑、かけられない……ダメな私は海にかえる\nそして、無口な二枚貝になる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going to cause‚ you any more trouble. So useless me‚\nis going to the sea‚ and I’m going to be like a silent clam…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14633.333333333336,
          "startTime": 36.56666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！？　これってヤバいんじゃ……\n急いで探さないと！　雫、早まるなよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha?! This is bad…\nI have to find her quickly. Shizuku! Don’t do anything hasty!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3833.3333333333358,
          "startTime": 45.63333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 47.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……またエサとられた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They stole my bait again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "魚にまで、嫌われてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the fish hate me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.3333333333344,
          "startTime": 55.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "探したぞ、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ I’ve been looking around for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん\nどうして、ここが分かったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san!\nHow did you know I was here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "よく星見市で釣りをしてるって話してただろ？\n一瞬、本気で焦ったぞ。こういうのは勘弁してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you often go fishing in Hoshimi City.\nI panicked there for a moment. Please‚ stop doing this kind of stuff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "一人で釣りをしながら\n静かに今後について考えようかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was trying to fish on my own‚\nso as to have some quiet time to think about the future…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "釣りが好きだとは聞いていたが……本当に好きなんだな\nそれでいい考えは浮かんだか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve heard you like fishing‚ and looks like you really do.\nSo‚ did you come up with anything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……魚にまで愛想つかされて\nヘコんでる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… even the fish are tired of me.\nI’m feeling down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "私はさくらちゃんみたいに明るくないし\n琴乃ちゃんみたいに強くもないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not bright and cheerful like Sakura-chan‚\nor tough like Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私がこのまま、アイドルしてていいのかなって\n……あ、またエサ取られた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know if it’s alright for me to carry on as an idol like this…\nAh! They stole my bait again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……その答えになるかどうかは分からないけど\n雫宛にファンレターが届いている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know whether this helps‚ but\nyou got a fan letter‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　サニピじゃなくて、私に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh? For me personally‚ not Sunny Peace?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、あくまでも、雫個人へのファンレターだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ it’s really a personal fan letter for you‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "一応、マネージャーの義務として中身は\nチェックさせてもらったけど、読んでみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I checked the content‚ because that’s my duty as a manager‚\nbut would you like to read it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "……読む。読みます。釣りは中断……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will. I’ll read it. I’ll take a break from fishing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、私はサニーピ―スが\n特に雫ちゃんが大好きな小学四年生です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Hello‚ I’m in my 4th year at elementary school and I really”\n“like Sunny Peace and particularly you‚ Shizuku-chan…”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 145.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "将来、私も雫ちゃんみたいな素敵なアイドルに\nなりたいのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“One day I want to be a super idol‚\njust like you‚ Shizuku-chan.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "周りの人達には、私なんかなれっこないから\n諦めろって言われちゃいます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“The people around me say someone like me could never\nbe one‚ so I should give up…”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "私は、歌もダンスも下手です。練習しても\n雫ちゃんみたいにうまくは出来ません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I’m no good at singing or dancing. Even when I practice‚\nI can’t get good like you…”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの言う通り、諦めた方がいいんでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Should I give up like everyone says I should?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "雫、君はその子になんて答える？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ how would you answer her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "……私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
